     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                            ParticleGun1 
                            ------------

 Generate several vertices and particles per event			    
 	
 1- Geometry construction
    ---------------------

 It is a simple box which represente an 'infinite' homogeneous medium.
  
 2- Physics list
    ------------

 PhysicsList.cc defines only geantino and transportation process.
         	
 3- Primary generator
    -----------------
 particle 1 : a geantino randomly uniform on a cylinder.
 particle 2 and 3 : on opposite to particle 1
   	
 4- Visualisation
    ------------- 
 Visualization Manager is set in the main().
 Initialisation of the drawing is done via the commands
 /vis/.. in the macro vis.mac. This macro is automatically read from the main 
 in case of interactive running mode.
 
 5- How to start ?
    --------------
 
  - compile and link to generate an executable
 	% cd gun
 	% gmake
 		
  - execute particleGun1 in 'interactive mode' with visualization
 	% particleGun1
 	....
 	Idle>      ---> type your commands. For instance:
	Idle> /run/beamOn 
	....
	Idle> /run/beamOn 3
	....				
 	Idle> exit
 		
  - execute particleGun1 in 'batch' mode from macro files
 	% ParticleGun1   run1.mac	
